article_title: Community Health Center celebrates arrival in Wareham

article_metadata.description: WAREHAM – With great fanfare, quality health care service for “underserved populations” has come to Wareham this week.The Greater New Bedford Community Health Center staged a ribbon-cutting ceremony Tuesday afternoon at its newest facility at 127 Marion Road in Wareham (at the front of Shaw’s Plaza) and nearly 100 staff members, dignitaries and center officials attended the hour-long dedication ceremony held outdoors in its parking lot.
